law.history: Repealed 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 393, sec. 51, effective July 15, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 155, sec. 104, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1974 Ky. Acts ch. 74, Art. VIII, K, sec. 1.

metadata.lrc-note: This section was amended by 1982 Acts Chapter 396, Section 4 and repealed by 1982 Acts Chapter 393, Section 51. Pursuant to KRS 446.260, the repeal prevails.
